{"tid":1613103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［水魔法師入］大象牙膏好似係高熱反應","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:07:48.000Z","uid":284565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7559ccd13e4092e199fd8ef38778778af04c23a4","tid":1613103,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"其實大家有無研究過乜係大象牙膏同埋實質用途。<br />\n<br />\nH2O2 (雙氧水）同埋 酵母粉溝水/ NaI （碘化鈉）溝埋之後會釋放大量氧氣同埋熱力，撈埋洗潔精/簡液 之後會出好多熱辣辣，不斷膨脹嘅泡泡，無反應曬嘅雙氧水甚至會刺激皮膚。<br />\n<br />\n呢個咁麻煩俾小朋友玩嘅實驗，其實有無 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">實質作用</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9c5c454a051e701a69b7c52efd1f372cb8dc86","tid":1613103,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"各位可以運用高中化學生物知識嚟對抗強權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb54bba91001f33f9a9d39cb9ad80ffa1837e164","tid":1613103,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"支裝可樂用萬樂珠點引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71607c5a91c5c4a3b9dad17f940ab925aed59552","tid":1613103,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"唔好咁複雜啦<br />\n用玻璃樽裝滿暗魔法掟出去夠用架啦<br />\n唔好搞咁多花臣，有效，快，易買為大前題"},{"pid":"5f5314e088dd32ba5b394e6c4e27af9f9492c7b5","tid":1613103,"uid":266935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}